item.title: Need some developers for a rs2006 re-make [delta base]
item.dc:creator: @Scully Scully
item.description:
@Scully wrote:

For just a second, let’s pretend that you do finish your remake of Runescape. Now, a lot of people are going to want to play it, that might be an issue. The way Delta is programmed, tossing everything in process for lulz, will basically grant you the ability to have the laggiest remake of all time. Don’t let that be a downer on your project though, you’ll at least be learning something. There are a lot of actual blank bases out there you could work off of. You might want to check out some of them, Hyperion, Runesource, Apollo, as they’re quite a bit more stable than delta.

[quote=“heatrn11, post:13, topic:430136”][quote author=mr extremez link=topic=532813.msg3911358#msg3911358 date=1328756528]

Hey watsup I happen to be a pretty good delta coder but how far do you plan on getting with this? Do you have a vps? Do you have small thinGs like you need to walk over rocks for the rock crabs to get up, 100% all skills. Pm me on moparscape forums and we can talk

You think i guy that posts 2 sentences for a developer has 100% all skills? Like honestly?

actually I just added a woodcutting base, and fishing base, so fish and woodcutting are both 88%
Thank you very much, I made a development ap sample in a earlier post btw.
So my server is comming along nicley.b

You mean you copied one? and were did you come up with the number 88 %?

Edit: omfg just realised i gravedug sry lawl.
[/quote]
I don’t copy sources used a black source called Blindscape, and all the tuts for skills you have to make a base, Which I obviously didn’t do, Keeping in Client.java because it’s more easy and not what people think. 88% because I don’t think it’s 100%. Thank you very much, now I am working on the object and item models Client base.[/quote]

Why the hell do you want to keep it in the client class, it’s such a mess already.
I’m trying to do my best on improving delta and keeping everything out of the client class,
and you dump it all in it because it’s “easier” lmao
